@node "important" "Some very important information!"



                                @{b}@{u}PLEASE NOTE@{ub}@{uu}

This index is "Do what you like"ware... Please feel free to @{"contact me" LINK CALL_ME}
to say you liked it, hated it, to send me a snapshot, request a POKE (oo-er!),
send a photo of any female you may know who has an undying love for a Scottish
Speccy hacker :-)

Seriously, I'm actually on the look out for any 128K music you may have,
especially if it's compatible with the AY player which was brought out for
DeliTracker a while back....

I'm also looking for a couple of the older copies of YS, so get in touch if you
have any you're selling :-)

Thanks,
Gerard.
@endnode
